high_descs: Turn around and go to the counter with the wine and tomato
Pick up the tomato from the counter
Turn around and go to the microwave by the refrigerator
Open the door, put the tomato in the microwave and close the door and turn microwave on. Open the door and remove the tomato
Turn to the left and face the counter to the right of the sink
Place the tomato on the counter between the sink and the cell phone
anns.task_desc: Put a microwaved tomato on the counter

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the counter containing the tomato.
Pick up the tomato from the counter.
Turn around and walk forward to the microwave.
Heat the tomato in the microwave for a few seconds, then take it out and close the microwave.
Turn left towards the cell phone on the counter.
Put the tomato on the counter, to the left of the cell phone.
anns.task_desc: Put a hot tomato on a counter top.

high_descs: Turn left and go toward the sink, then turn left to face the counter with the tomato on it.
Pick up the tomato from the counter.
Turn around and go to the microwave.
Open the microwave, put the tomato in the microwave and heat it up, then take the tomato out.
Turn left to face the counter above the dishwasher.
Place the tomato on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm tomato on the counter.
